subject: Rugby (Game)
lead_paragraph: England, the defending champion, defeated Tonga, 36-20, to advance to the quarterfinals of the World Cup in Paris. England faced the prospect of becoming the first defending champion to fail to reach the quarterfinals. But after a dominating performance, the English will play Australia in Marseille on Oct. 6 in a rematch of the 2003 final.
